rComments: One of the best teachers I've ever had. Clearly simplifies  even the most complex concepts. Cares about developing his students. Combines extensive practical management consulting experience with academic depth.

Professors who know their stuff inside out make all subjects easy. Professors who don't know their stuff make it confusing. See the movie "stand up and deliver". There a Calculus professor made calculus so easy all his students got A's in national exams. Inept professors suspected fraud!

UOT's attitude towards CSC340 part time instructors is deplorable. Funding is inadequate and results in instructors having no choice but to cut down on time spent on preparation. While the course started with great enthusiasm, it became uninteresting when dollar value of time reached nil.
Easiest final exam I've ever had!
He made this course sooooo easy. Thank You.
